channel.title: 1st time making a server, run.bat error
channel.description:
Hi, I'm as new as it gets to making servers although I have played them for years. So, could someone please help. Even if it's the simplest thing :o dont make fun of me.
It does this with every source and client:( please help
[IMG]http://img171.imageshack.us/img171/1133/helpmee.png[/img]
[IMG]http://img528.imageshack.us/img528/1761/helpmeee.png[/img]

item.title: 1st time making a server, run.bat error
item.dc:creator: @ilovecoke ilovecoke
item.description:
@ilovecoke wrote:

Loveandpower:

A lot of people don’t realize this is due to 508 maps. They try to unpack the files before they have been unzipped…or I may have that backwards either way…it has to do with 508 maps…

fixed it thank you!
